quirks.name: Fiery Form
quirks.description: The Kaiju can be perpetually wreathed in flame, or it may be be activated by anger or injury

quirks.name: Icy Form
quirks.description: The Kaiju may have a coating of ice, or may “ice up” when threatened

quirks.name: Horns
quirks.description: In addition to any horns or antlers the Kaiju may normally have, it also has additional horns or other bony or chitinous protuberances.

quirks.name: Metallic Exterior
quirks.description: The Kaiju has metallic plates on its exterior or its skin or hide is made of metal.

quirks.name: Extra Limbs
quirks.description: The Kaiju had d6 extra arms or legs.

quirks.name: Prehensile tongue
quirks.description: The Kaiju has a long tongue that can constrict around opponents or be used as an attack.

quirks.name: Extra Eyes
quirks.description: The Kaiju has d6 extra eyes on its head or other body parts.

quirks.name: Stinger
quirks.description: The Kaiju has a poisonous stinger on an appendage or in an orifice.

quirks.name: Extra Head
quirks.description: The Kaiju has a duplicate head somewhere on it’s body.

quirks.name: Tentacles
quirks.description: The Kaiju has d4 tentacles on its body.

quirks.name: Suction Cups
quirks.description: The Kaiju has suction cups on its extremities allowing for grappling and/or wall crawling.

quirks.name: Wings
quirks.description: The Kaiju has wings allowing for flight.

quirks.name: Zombie
quirks.description: The Kaiju is undead, reanimated by scientific means.

quirks.name: Metamorphosis
quirks.description: The Kaiju can undergo a metamorphosis allowing it to take on a larger and more powerful form

quirks.name: Rocky Exterior
quirks.description: The Kaiju has a rough and hard exterior that may be chipped away over time.

quirks.name: robotic components
quirks.description: The Kaiju has been modified with cybernetic components to replace damaged body parts or upgrade its abilities

quirks.name: tail
quirks.description: The Kaiju has a tail or additional tail that can be used for extra locomotion or attacking.

quirks.name: fog
quirks.description: The Kaiju can emit a thick fog at will or when under threat
